'''Belecthor''' is [[Sindarin]] for "Mighty Eagle", and can refer to:

* [[Belecthor I]] ({{TA|2545}} - {{TA|2655|n}}), the fifteenth [[Ruling Steward]] of [[Gondor]].
* [[Belecthor II]] ({{TA|2752}} - {{TA|2872|n}}), the twenty-first [[Ruling Steward]] of [[Gondor]].
